=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我是否做了小三？我是否應同佢講清楚並劃清界線？ 但以後仲要?公司見面 好尷尬? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dcd93c5ee605d790265d6c85977695c6db3fd7","tid":26654,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"d真毒撚過晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9c35df79cd22acd966e193798a1ea7324ac1b3","tid":26654,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e188f70b66e2260fd0e75a3ee2e0eeac32ac66cd","tid":26654,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:27:24.000Z","msg":"唔好問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不嬲都多單身狗"},{"pid":"7216abc32cac8ad961ef27e85351744cdbe298ef","tid":26654,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7f57b166d385bc202fdbd30b1f5ddb2c67907d4","tid":26654,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89084a0fd8822dde8bbb60a41b4bad76e05ce620","tid":26654,"uid":18588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"因為就黎性誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}